## translation_html
\f1 \

\f0 The purpose is to enable anyone without html skills to translate in is language.
\f1 \

\f0 We use gettext to generate a new html file with string of characters translated from the \'ab\'a0walkthrough.html\'a0\'bb file.
\f1 \

\f0 You can help translating in your language all the string of characters, they all are in \'ab\'a0base.po\'a0\'bb.
\f1 \

\f0 To generate the html, open \'ab\'a0config\'a0\'bb, install python3 if needed. Then install packages needed and create .po and .mo following the instruction. 
\f1 \

\f0 Then, in \'ab\'a0translation.py\'a0\'bb, please modify all the \'ab\'a0fr\'a0\'bb according to your language.
\f1 \

\f0 Finally run the file. A \'ab\'a0fr.hmtl\'a0\'bb file is generated in \'ab\'a0translation_html\'a0\'bb. 
\f1 \

